title: make.bash: ld warnings with clang trunk
body:
% uname -a
Darwin 186095.local 13.0.0 Darwin Kernel Version 13.0.0: Thu Sep 19 22:22:27 PDT 2013;
root:xnu-2422.1.72~6/RELEASE_X86_64 x86_64
% $CC --version
clang version 3.5 (trunk 201493)
% cd `go env GOROOT`/src
% ./make.bash
Output:
https://gist.github.com/fsouza/9035330/raw/96452454cda9c1609d4bf2a703146a825595eebb/gistfile1.txt

It works nicely with Apple clang 5.0 (which is clang 3.3).
